data.description: SELLER WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE TOWARD BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS, TITLE EXPENSES, OR RATE BUY DOWN. Beautiful all brick home positioned on large cove lot. Enjoy the benefits of having all bedrooms located on main floor with an enormous bonus room upstairs, perfect for all your entertaining needs! Hardwood floors and granite countertops in kitchen. Extra tall ceilings give a spacious feel throughout the home. Home has been loved and well maintained. 2021 new insulated garage doors installed. Roof installed 2020. The interior has been freshly painted.
